bc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Viet Nam xac lap ky tich lich su sau tran hoa Jordan hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam x\u00e1c l\u1eadp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Jordan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-DT-Viet-Nam-1-1-Jordan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam x\u00e1c l\u1eadp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed kh\u00f4ng thua \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jordan c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 thanh tho\u00e1t v\u00e0 l\u1ea5n \u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong hi\u1ec7p 1. V\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ed3n \u00e9p khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sang hi\u1ec7p 2, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eadm l\u1ea1i do suy y\u1ebfu v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Jordan c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 \u1edf ph\u00fat 71 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Jordan, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 100 tr\u00ean BXH FIFA.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m vui nho nh\u1ecf l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd v\u1eeba x\u00e1c l\u1eadp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Jordan. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn x\u00e1c l\u1eadp nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o khi tham d\u1ef1 m\u1ed9t v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i c\u1ea5p ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/dtqg-c292-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span> t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi 2 th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 h\u00f2a (Jordan c\u00f3 3 th\u1eafng, 3 h\u00f2a). Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i khi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang 3 b\u00e0n sau 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Jordan (0-0), Afghanistan (0-0) v\u00e0 Campuchia (5-0). Khi h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ghi 9 b\u00e0n/ 6 tr\u1eadn (7 b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Campuchia), s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a \u0111\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c sau 12 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch v\u00e0o l\u00fac 12h00 h\u00f4m nay gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00fac 7h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai 29/3.<br>\r\n<p><em><strong>Highlight Jordan 1-1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (V\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019)</strong></em></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/3/28/Highlight-Jordan-vs-Viet-Nam.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><img src=\"http://cms.bongda24h.vn/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 220px;\"></div>\r\n<p>Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\" style=\"text-align: start;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"http://cms.bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-ca-ngoi-cac-hoc-tro-sau-tran-hoa-jordan-168-182971.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/23/hlv-park-hang-seo-ca-ngoi-cac-hoc-tro-sau-tran-hoa-jordan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"http://cms.bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-ca-ngoi-cac-hoc-tro-sau-tran-hoa-jordan-168-182971.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo khen ng\u1ee3i c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Jordan</span><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 27/3, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Jordan. Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Abu Amara...</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div st