n\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft Asian Cup 2019?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 27/3, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Jordan tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, s\u1ef1 thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ee7 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Jordan, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng tan m\u1ed9ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 80 tr\u00ean BXH FIFA th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf VCK ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2019.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Viet Nam\" title=\"\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/dt-viet-nam-xac-lap-ky-tich-lich-su-sau-tran-hoa-jordan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf nh\u00f3m 3 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft Asian Cup 2019</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 4 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. V\u1edbi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Jordan, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ee9ng ngay tr\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0 Li-b\u0103ng, Oman hay Qatar \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo BXH FIFA th\u00e1ng 3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/dtqg-c292-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span> \u0111ang x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 16 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. V\u00e0 trong th\u00e1ng 4 t\u1edbi, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. V\u00ec v\u1eady, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng Asian Cup 2019.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00e1c \u0110T \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9, Qatar, Oman, Turkmenistan, Kyrgyzstan. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ban \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1ebd c\u00f3 sau khi FIFA c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 BXH th\u00e1ng 4.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khu v\u1ef1c \u0110N\u00c1, v\u1edbi th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u1ea3 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 Philippines \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi \u1edf nh\u00f3m 4.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>Nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi t\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019 (</strong></em><b><i>Trong ngo\u1eb7c l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i):</i></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00f3m 1: UAE (ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 - 405), Iran (727), Australia (700), Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n (528), H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (520), Saudi Arabia (445)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00f3m 2: Trung Qu\u1ed1c (431), Kyrgyzstan (424), Syria (423), Lebanon (404), Palestine (401), Oman (383)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00f3m 3: Uzbekistan (381), Iraq (381), \u1ea4n \u0110\u1ed9 (354), Qatar (339), Vi\u1ec7t Nam (331), Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean (292)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00f3m 4: Philippines (289), Bahrain (281), Jordan (272), Yemen (250), Th\u00e1i Lan (243), Turkmenistan (242)</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<p><em><strong>Highlight Jordan 1-1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (V\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019)</strong></em></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/3/28/Highlight-Jordan-vs-Viet-Nam.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><img src=\"http://cms.bongda24h.vn/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 220px;\"></div>\r\n<p>Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\" style=\"text-align: start;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"http://cms.bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-ca-ngoi-cac-hoc-tro-sau-tran-hoa-jordan-168-182971.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/23/hlv-park-hang-seo-ca-ngoi-cac-hoc-tro-sau-tran-hoa-jordan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"http://cms.bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-ca-ngoi-cac-hoc-tro-sau-tran-hoa-jordan-168-182971.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo khen ng\u1ee3i c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Jordan</span><br>\r\nT\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 27/3, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Jordan. Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 trong hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Abu Amara...</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"550","checkdouble":"182977"},{"date":"08:07 28/03","title":"Th\u00eam th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/them-thong-tin-ve-chan-thuong-cua-thu-thanh-dang-van-lam.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6p