0e2n c\u1ee7a Jordan. D\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 song c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn binh \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c trong hi\u1ec7p 1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tuy nhi\u00ean sau \u0111\u00f3 Jordan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 sau nh\u1eefng pha uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Tu\u1ea5n M\u1ea1nh trong hi\u1ec7p 2. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 \u0110TVN ch\u01a1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ng\u1ee3i khen.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bao chi Jordan noi gi ve loi choi cua DT Viet Nam hinh anh\" title=\"B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Jordan n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Bao-chi-Jordan-noi-gi-ve-loi-choi-cua-DT-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Jordan khen \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Jordan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, t\u1edd b\u00e1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Jordan Kooora.com \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong hi\u1ec7p 1. &quot;\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho Jordan b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. H\u1ecd cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c&quot;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kooora.com c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong hi\u1ec7p 2 khi\u1ebfn Jordan ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a nh\u1edd c\u00fa s\u00fat th\u1eed v\u1eadn may c\u1ee7a Amarah.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y,&nbsp; trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a AFC c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo. AFC c\u0169ng ch\u00fac m\u1eebng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai tham d\u1ef1 Asian Cup sau l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 11 n\u0103m.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edd b\u00e1o ch\u00e2u \u00c1 FOX Sports Asia \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m. V\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 1-1 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh \u0111\u00fang nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/dtqg-c292-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span> \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o v\u1edbi 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. Ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbt 3 b\u00e0n trong 6 tr\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>Highlight Jordan 1-1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (V\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019)</strong></em></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/3/28/Highlight-Jordan-vs-Viet-Nam.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"http://cms.bongda24h.vn/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 220px;\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-jordan-bat-ngo-voi-loi-choi-cua-dt-viet-nam-168-182973.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/hlv-jordan-bat-ngo-voi-loi-choi-cua-dt-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-jordan-bat-ngo-voi-loi-choi-cua-dt-viet-nam-168-182973.html\">HLV Jordan b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Jordan Jamal Abu-Abed cho bi\u1ebft b\u1ecb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi s\u1edbm b\u1ecb \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi trong hi\u1ec7p 1.</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"548","checkdouble":"182981"},{"date":"09:48 28/03","title":"Chuy\u00ean gia Vi\u1ec7t n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i Jordan?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/28/chuyen-gia-viet-noi-gi-ve-tran-hoa-cua-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-tai-jordan.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regu