le=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truoc nhung tin don, Arsene Wenger phat bieu ve PSG hinh anh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n, Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/Truoc-nhung-tin-don,-Arsene-Wenger-phat-bieu-ve-PSG-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ef1u HLV Sevilla th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. 2 m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Emery d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 Champions League, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1edfi Barca c\u00f2n m\u00f9a n\u00e0y b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1edfi Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng g\u00ec Emery th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn BL\u0110 PSG h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch sa th\u1ea3i nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/nhung-hlv-co-the-thay-the-emery-dan-dat-psg-197-182878.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>5 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay th\u1ebf Emery</strong></span> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, \u00e1n sa th\u1ea3i \u0111ang l\u01a1 l\u1eedng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Sevilla.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Arsene Wenger khuy\u00ean PSG ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o Unai Emery</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Wenger c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/psg-104.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>PSG</strong></span> \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao cho \u00f4ng n\u00e0y, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n, Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 PSG, \u00f4ng khuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Emery.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"wenger\" title=\"wenger\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/16/wenger-tiet-lo-cai-ten-co-the-giup-psg-thanh-cong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n theo d\u00f5i t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 PSG, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Unai Emery. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 PSG, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p n\u00ean nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Emery: \u201cH\u1ecd c\u1ea7n nhanh ch\u00f3ng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Emery, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi ti\u1ebft cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n Emery \u1edf l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7\u00a0c\u1ee7a PSG\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/huan-luyen-vien/arsene-wenger-4.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Wenger</strong></span>, c\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund, Thomas Tuchel c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a PSG. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u00f4ng n\u00e0y t\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"545","checkdouble":"182944"},{"date":"06:31 28/03","title":"Pogba l\u1eadp chi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi cho Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/pogba-lap-chien-cong-tren-dt-phap-va-dau-hoi-cho-mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(No