1ea1o tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Pogba cho th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 r\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong th\u1eddi gian qua, anh m\u1ea5t \u0111i ni\u1ec1m tin n\u01a1i HLV Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ngo\u00e0i n\u00f3i l\u00ean r\u1eb1ng anh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u00f2n ch\u1ec9 ra s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t c\u1eadp trong c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Mourinho t\u1ea1i CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba lap ky luc tren DT Phap va dau hoi cho Mourinho hinh anh\" title=\"Pogba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c tr\u00ean \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi cho Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Pogba-tren-DT-Phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c tr\u00ean \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga, <span href=\"bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-utd-da-mua-pogba-voi-gia-beo-bot-172-182819.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Paul Pogba</strong></span> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Didier Deschamps b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, ngang v\u1edbi Adrien Rabiot v\u00e0 N\u2019golo Kante. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, ch\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n tuy\u1ec7t h\u1ea3o cho Kylian Mbappe b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 ph\u00fat, l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Pogba \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho Ph\u00e1p. Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u00e0ng trai g\u1ed1c Guinea v\u1eeba ghi b\u00e0n, v\u1eeba ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. V\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c Pogba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c tr\u00ean \u0110T Ph\u00e1p trong l\u1ea7n 51 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi anh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 hy v\u1ecdng Pogba s\u1ebd mang phong \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U \u1edf ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Premier League v\u00e0 FA Cup. Mourinho ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Swansea cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Nga 1-3 Ph\u00e1p (Giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf):</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/3/28/18ndv.MP4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-nga-13-phap-giao-huu-quoc-te-329-182964.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nga 1-3 Ph\u00e1p (Giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-nga-vs-phap-22h50-ngay-273-giao-huu-quoc-te-372-182948.html\">Nga 1-3 Ph\u00e1p: Th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/lich-su-world-cup/zidane-va-scandal-huyen-thoai-tai-vck-world-cup-2006-441-182778.html\">Zidane v\u00e0 scandal huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2006</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/phap-23-colombia-pogba-du-bi-les-bleus-thua-nguoc-tren-san-nha-184-182723.html\">Ph\u00e1p 2-3 Colombia: Pogba d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, Les Bleus thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-phap-23-colombia-giao-huu-quoc-te-331-182720.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 2-3 Colombia (Giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"544","checkdouble":"182970"},{"date":"06:54 28/03","title":"Thi\u1ebfu Messi, Argentina b\u1ecb T\u00e2y Ban Nha gieo n\u1ed7i nh\u1ee5c tr\u0103m n\u0103m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/thieu-messi-argentina-bi-tay-ban-nha-gieo-noi-nhuc-tram-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0