1-6. Trong \u0111\u00f3, Isco l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u201ct\u00e0n nh\u1eabn\u201d nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick trong khi Diego Costa, Thiago Alcantara v\u00e0 Iago Aspas m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi 1 b\u00e0n. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Nicolas Otamendi ch\u1eb3ng b\u00f5 b\u00e8n g\u00ec khi c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Argentina that bai dam nhat lich su truoc Tay Ban Nha hinh anh\" title=\"Argentina th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Argentina-that-thu-1-6-truoc-TBN.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Argentina th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u01a1i b\u00e0y nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Argentina ngay c\u1ea3 khi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i. B\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a La Albiceleste qu\u00e1 mong manh. \u0110i l\u00ean tr\u00ean, c\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu g\u1eafn k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nguy hi\u1ec3m khi m\u00e0 World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 3 th\u00e1ng l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi tranh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 chi ti\u1ebft Argentina th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-tay-ban-nha-vs-argentina-2h30-ngay-283-giao-huu-quoc-te-372-182954.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>thua 1-6 tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha</strong></span>, h\u1ecd t\u1eebng ch\u1ecbu n\u1ed7i nh\u1ee5c t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ti\u1ec7p Kh\u1eafc t\u1ea1i\u00a0 World Cup 1958 v\u00e0 Bolivia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i World Cup 2010. Argentina c\u0169ng t\u1eebng thua Colombia 0-5 v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1993. Ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd, h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn h\u01a1n th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\n\u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i vang d\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Argentina ch\u1ec9 sau 6 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00eam th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Isco, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1eadp hat-trick tr\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1eddng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb Confed Cup 2013 t\u1edbi nay, T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi 3 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u T\u00e2y Ban Nha 6-1 Argentina (Giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf):</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/3/28/tbn-vs-argentina.MP4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-tay-ban-nha-61-argentina-giao-huu-quoc-te-331-182967.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: T\u00e2y Ban Nha 6-1 Argentina (Giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-tay-ban-nha-vs-argentina-2h30-ngay-283-giao-huu-quoc-te-372-182954.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha 6-1 Argentina: V\u1eafng Messi, Albiceleste th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-tuc-world-cup/lionel-messi-chang-can-ai-day-them-dieu-gi-439-182927.html\">Lionel Messi ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ai d\u1ea1y th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/sao-tuyen-tbn-rat-kho-de-ngan-chan-messi-184-182884.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n TBN: R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/khong-vo-dich-world-cup-lionel-messi-se-bi-ban-421-182826.html\">Kh\u00f4ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup, Lionel Messi s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ... b\u1eafn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-tuc-world-cup/hlv-sampaoli-phat-bieu-ve-dt-argentina-439-182764.html\">HLV Sampaoli ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Argentina</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"543","checkdouble":"182972"},{"date":"07:53 28/03","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 28/3: M.U ch\u1ed1t h\u1ea1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/25/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-283-mu-chot-ha-tuong-lai-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSa