ng nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Pogba c\u00f2n h\u1eefu \u00edch v\u1edbi M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem tin bong da sang ngay 283 MU chot ha tuong lai Pogba hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 283 MU ch\u1ed1t h\u1ea1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-283-MU-chot-ha-tuong-lai-Pogba-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pogba v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam x\u00e1c l\u1eadp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Jordan. </strong>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Jordan \u1edf tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u qua 27/3, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c l\u1eadp k\u1ef3 t\u00edch l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c&nbsp; kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o khi tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i c\u00f2n c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang 3 b\u00e0n sau 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>HLV Jordan b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam. </strong>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Jordan, Jamal Abu-Abed cho bi\u1ebft b\u1ecb b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi s\u1edbm b\u1ecb \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi trong hi\u1ec7p 1. C\u00e1ch nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Real s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thanh l\u00fd sao s\u00e1ng. </strong>Real Madrid v\u00e0 Isco m\u1edbi th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd r\u1eddi CLB trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Isco trong m\u00f9a 2017/18 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam ngu\u1ed3n ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed5 sung nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, Real s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Chelsea hay Man City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Isco the hien phong do tam thuong\" title=\"Isco the hien phong do tam thuong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Real-Madrid-ban-tien-ve-Isco-trong-mua-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Isco \u0111ang r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda r\u1eddi Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>3 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Dembele. </strong>Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Don Balon, c\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Atletico Madrid, Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool. C\u1ea3 3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ho\u1eb7c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t \u0111i nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh (l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Griezmann, Sanchez, Coutinho) v\u00e0 xem sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Juventus gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c.</strong> Theo Gazzetta dello Sport, Juventus hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Jonas Hector c\u1ee7a Cologne. CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t nguy c\u01a1 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra, Juve hay nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh nh\u01b0 Dortmund hay Bayern Munich s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a l\u00e0 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Hector\" title=\"hau ve Hector\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/3/29/Doi-hinh-tieu-bieu-luot-di-vong-loai-World-Cup-2018-khu-vuc-chau-Au-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hector \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 mua Donnarumma.</strong> Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Liverpool, Steve Nicol m\u1edbi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 CLB c\u0169 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Gianluigi Donnarumma c\u1ee7a AC Milan. C\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y tin r\u1eb1ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 19 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o, s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho The Kop trong c\u1ea3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu gia nh\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Real ra gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho Bale.</strong> Real Madrid m\u1edbi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Gareth Bale ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro tr\u1edf l\u00ean. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u cho Real m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00f4ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"542","checkdouble":"182978"},{"date":"09:40 28/03","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a MU ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/romero-chan-thuong-o-tran-tay-ban-nha-vs-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-