ground:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Sergio Romero c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Argentina sau pha va ch\u1ea1m m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi Diego Costa \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 22.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thu mon Romero chan thuong o tran Tay Ban Nha vs Argentina hinh anh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Romero ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/romero-chan-thuong-o-tran-tay-ban-nha-vs-argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Romero ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/de-gea-romero-xung-dang-duoc-ra-san-nhieu-hon-172-177318.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Romero</span> \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t hi\u1ebfm hoi sau khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi De Gea t\u1ea1i Old Trafford m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Tuy v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u00e3 \u0111en \u0111\u1ee7i g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ec9 sau 22 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 12, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eadp nh\u1ea3 v\u1edbi nhau kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Diego Costa. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o g\u1ed1c Brazil lao v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0 t\u1ea1i Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3, Romero \u0111\u00e3 lao ra v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Diego Costa ghi b\u00e0n. Hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 va ch\u1ea1m kh\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n l\u00e0 Costa c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n m\u1ed9t l\u00fac l\u00e2u. Anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129 trong v\u00e0i ph\u00fat v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRomero c\u0169ng g\u1eafng g\u01b0\u1ee3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm. 10 ph\u00fat sau pha va ch\u1ea1m, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thay ra v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 anh l\u00e0 Caballero.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Romero kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Man United v\u00e0 Swansea cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng sao tr\u1ebb Joel Pereira s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfm v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Romero tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-283-mu-chot-ha-tuong-lai-pogba-184-182978.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/25/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-283-mu-chot-ha-tuong-lai-pogba.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-283-mu-chot-ha-tuong-lai-pogba-184-182978.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 28/3: M.U ch\u1ed1t h\u1ea1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Pogba</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 28/3.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f2n ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Argentina. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Man United l\u00e0 De Gea c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a \u201cB\u00f2 t\u00f3t\u201d. Anh ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 1 l\u1ea7n khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Otamendi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00f9 l\u1ea1i, De Gea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p m\u1ed9t pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p. Anh c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng si\u00eau d\u00e0i t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a La Albiceleste \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho Iago Aspas. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a De Gea, Man United th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef khung th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (Bongda24h)</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"541","checkdouble":"182982"},{"date":"10:11 28/03","title":"C\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Anh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd m\u1ea1nh mi\u1ec7ng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/28/cam-hoa-anh-nguoi-y-manh-mieng-dap-tra-du-luan.JPG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:la