lack;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Luigi Di Baggio m\u1ea1nh mi\u1ec7ng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu Anh 1-1 \u00dd.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/truc-tiep-anh-vs-italia-02h00-ngay-283-giao-huu-quoc-te-184-182952.html\">Anh 1-1 \u00dd</span> t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i may m\u1eafn cho Azzurri v\u1edbi pha g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a Lorenzo Insigne. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR khi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng tin r\u1eb1ng Italia x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00fa s\u00fat penalty \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Di Baggio manh mieng dap tra du luan sau tran Anh 1-1 Y hinh anh\" title=\"HLV Di Baggio m\u1ea1nh mi\u1ec7ng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn sau tr\u1eadn Anh 1-1 \u00dd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/cam-hoa-anh-nguoi-y-manh-mieng-dap-tra-du-luan.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">HLV Luigi Di Baggio m\u1ea1nh mi\u1ec7ng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu Anh 1-1 \u00dd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u00f3i chung, Italia v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd sau th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Wembley, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Luigi Di Baggio nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1eeba b\u1ecb T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00f9i d\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn 6-1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV t\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n n\u00e0y v\u1eabn m\u1ea1nh mi\u1ec7ng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau tr\u1eadn Anh 1-1 \u00dd: \u201cT\u00f4i m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110TQG ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 10 ng\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec qu\u00fd v\u1ecb hay ch\u00ea bai, ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n cho m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec3n \u00dd t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi h\u01a1n v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Italia v\u00e0 m\u00ecnh lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 t\u00e0i.\u201d</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/truc-tiep-anh-vs-italia-02h00-ngay-283-giao-huu-quoc-te-184-182952.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/truc-tiep-anh-vs-italia-02h00-ngay-283-giao-huu-quoc-te.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/truc-tiep-anh-vs-italia-02h00-ngay-283-giao-huu-quoc-te-184-182952.html\">Anh 1-1 Italia: VAR v\u00e0 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Tarkowski</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Vardy, nh\u01b0ng sai l\u1ea7m trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Tarkowski khi\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u1ec3 Italia c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wembley.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-tuyen-anh-van-menh-trong-tay-nhung-nguoi-ngoai-quoc-421-182887.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/24/doi-tuyen-anh-van-menh-trong-tay-nhung-nguoi-ngoai-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-tuyen-anh-van-menh-trong-tay-nhung-nguoi-ngoai-quoc-421-182887.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh: V\u1eadn m\u1ec7nh trong tay nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u1ea1i qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nT\u1eebng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n d\u0103m ba giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i v\u00e0 c\u1eaft qu\u00e3ng n\u1ed5i d\u1eady l\u00e0n s\u00f3ng tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB h\u1ea1ng trung \u1edf Premier League...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/lich-su-world-cup/world-cup-1934-phat-xit-bong-da-va-azzuri-441-182620.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/22/world-cup-1934-phat-xit-bong-da-va-azzuri.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/lich-su-world-cup/world-cup-1934-phat-xit-bong-da-va-azzuri-441-182620.html\">World Cup 1934: Ph\u00e1t x\u00edt, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 Azzurri</span><br>\r\nN\u0103m 1934, khi ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c kinh t\u1ebf v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb sau h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a Th\u1ebf chi\u1ebfn th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t, Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00f4...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\n<br>\r\nHighlights tr\u1eadn Anh 1-1 \u00dd:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/3/28/qhvzg.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gia Khoa \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h<o:p></o:p></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"540","checkdouble":"182986"},{"date":"17:40 27/03","title":"Marcos Alonso c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/25/marcos-alonso-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-t