 color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real Madrid mua Marcos Alonso th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Los Blancos.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mua Marcos Alonso</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu Marcelo, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng n\u0103m nay anh \u0111\u00e3 30 tu\u1ed5i m\u00e0 Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mua Marcos Alonso Sao Chelsea phan ung ra sao hinh anh\" title=\"Real Madrid mua Marcos Alonso Sao Chelsea ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ra sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/16/Real-Madrid-mua-Marcos-Alonso-Sao-Chelsea-phan-ung-ra-sao-hinh-anh.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid mua Marcos Alonso \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nReal Madrid mua <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/marcos-alonso-52705.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Marcos Alonso</strong></span> \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. HLV Zidane \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Los Blancos chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Bernabeu. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Alonso \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Premier League trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t m\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng hay x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a anh mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n cho Chelsea. Ngo\u00e0i Real th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/messi-muon-barca-mua-hau-ve-chelsea-180-182426.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Barca quan t\u00e2m Alonso</strong></span>, c\u1ea3 Messi v\u00e0 Pique \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Marcos Alonso c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup v\u00e0 v\u00e0o Top 4 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. T\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alonso va Morata cua Chelsea\" title=\"Alonso va Morata cua Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/5/chelsea-don-tin-mung-tu-marcos-alonso-truoc-tran-gap-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alonso kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Real c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00ecnh hay kh\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. T\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n. T\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Stamford Bridge, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i r\u1eddi n\u01a1i n\u00e0y\u201d, Alonso ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlonso ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/chelsea-6.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Chelsea</strong></span> l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, ngo\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u00ec Eden Hazard v\u00e0 Thibaut Courtois c\u1ee7a The Blues c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Los Blancos quan t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Marcos Alonso \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/69408-40942/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Marcos Alonso \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"539","checkdouble":"182943"},{"date":"21:31 27/03","title":"Real h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 Bale ra \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/22/real-het-gia-khung-de-bale-ra-di.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bo