ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid s\u1ebd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Gareth Bale n\u1ebfu thu v\u1ec1 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9 c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u1edf k\u1ef3 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018, cho d\u00f9 anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n t\u1edbi n\u0103m 2022 v\u1edbi Los Blancos.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real het gia de Bale ra di - chuyen nhuong real Madrid hinh anh\" title=\"Real h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 Bale ra \u0111i - chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/22/Real-het-gia-de-Bale-ra-di---chuyen-nhuong-real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Bale</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd AS, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e1n th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t b\u00e1n Gareth Bale trong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean Real Madrid s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Gareth Bale ra \u0111i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1eebng b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 mua ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Tottenham h\u1ed3i n\u0103m 2013.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Bale, c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u1edf Madrid v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 29 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Spurs hay \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Chelsea m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn&nbsp;Manchester United.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Bale nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb PSG v\u00e0 Chelsea,&nbsp;nh\u01b0ng anh \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Man United,&quot;&nbsp;nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha - Eduardo Inda ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u00ean Chiringuito TV.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 101 tri\u1ec7u euro, Bale li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. \u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 29 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n c\u00f9ng Real Madrid, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Roboto;&#10;mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"538","checkdouble":"182957"},{"date":"07:30 28/03","title":"N\u00f3ng: Real Madrid s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thanh l\u00fd sao s\u00e1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/24/nong-real-madrid-san-sang-thanh-ly-sao-sang.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-botto