black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m, kh\u00f4ng ai ng\u1edd ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i \u0111ang l\u00e2m v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh b\u1ecb Real Madrid h\u1eaft h\u1ee7i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra\u2026</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e0n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/5-cau-thu-real-muon-day-isco-ra-di-180-180497.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real Madrid v\u00e0 Isco</strong></span> \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd: Kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Isco m\u00f9a 2017/18 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i, tr\u00e1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. V\u00e0 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n th\u00eam v\u1ed1n li\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i t\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, Real kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Theo Bongda24h.vn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Isco.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid ban tien ve Isco trong mua he 2018 hinh anh\" title=\"Real Madrid b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Isco trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Real-Madrid-ban-tien-ve-Isco-trong-mua-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Isco th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3><strong>Isco kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh</strong></h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Isco tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ee9u tinh c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i \u201cC\u1eadu b\u00e9 v\u00e0ng\u201d n\u0103m 2012 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia \u0111i t\u1edbi c\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Qua \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch La Liga v\u00e0 Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Isco t\u1ea1i Real c\u0169ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3. Thay v\u00ec d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u201ch\u1ea1ng sang\u201d, anh chi\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Bernabeu khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 kh\u1edfi tranh. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng Cristiano Ronado, Karim Benzema \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t sa s\u00fat c\u00f2n Gareth Bale ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u00ean mi\u00ean, Isco c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/5-cau-thu-real-muon-day-isco-ra-di-180-180497.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/9/5-cau-thu-real-muon-day-isco-ra-di.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/5-cau-thu-real-muon-day-isco-ra-di-180-180497.html\">5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y Isco ra \u0111i</span><br>\r\n<span>Theo Diario Gol, c\u00f3 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Isco kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 m\u01a1, Isco th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i t\u1edbi g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i v\u00f2ng lu\u1ea9n qu\u1ea9n, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Malaga gi\u1edd l\u1ea1i m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh khi Ronaldo, Benzema hay Bale tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<h3>Real Madrid b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Isco</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh Real Madrid b\u1ecb Barcelona b\u1ecf xa t\u1ea1i La Liga v\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/real-luc-duc-chuyen-nhuong-man-city-tinh-cuom-isco-172-179791.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Isco</strong></span> l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ee9c b\u1ed1i. \u00d4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap s\u1ee9c cho Real t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i. \u1ea4y v\u1eady m\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Real nh\u01b0 Isco l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"perez\" title=\"perez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/3/Sao-Bayern-tha-thinh-thanh-cong-2-dai-gia-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Isco</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCon s\u1ed1 ch\u1ec9 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 36 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 qua tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00f9a n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Isco l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. HLV Zinedine Zidane c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m 1992.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p song ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0: Real Madrid b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Isco ngay trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n thu v\u1ec1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 80 t\u1edbi 90 tri\u1ec7u Euro s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Los Blancos thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n trong cu\u1ed9c c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Isco. Hai \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/choang-vang-voi-so-tien-man-city-dung-de-mua-isco-180-182894.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City</strong></span> l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u00ed d\u1ee5 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 