g.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3><strong>Dembele: K\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u, th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng b\u1ea5y nhi\u00eau</strong></h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar d\u1ee9t \u00e1o t\u1edbi PSG khi\u1ebfn k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Barcelona b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea3o l\u1ed9n. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 trong tay s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 222 tri\u1ec7u Euro ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng b\u1ed1i r\u1ed1i trong t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Sau khi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, Barca nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Ousmane Dembele c\u1ee7a Dortmund v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb 20 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Day! Danh tinh 3 CLB mua Ousmane Dembele cua Barca hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e2y! Danh t\u00ednh 3 CLB mua Ousmane Dembele c\u1ee7a Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/day-danh-tinh-3-clb-mua-ousmane-dembele-cua-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Dembele \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1i gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 Barca ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 r\u1ebb: 105 tri\u1ec7u Euro ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 40 tri\u1ec7u ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed t\u00f9y th\u00e0nh t\u00edch Dembele trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t m\u1eaft x\u00edch ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o thay Neymar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 tr\u1eadn, Dembele \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo, ngh\u1ec9 4 th\u00e1ng tr\u1eddi. Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t, ngh\u1ec9 th\u00eam 1 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 sau nh\u1eefng tai n\u1ea1n \u0111\u00f3, phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Dembele l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ph\u1eadp ph\u00f9. V\u00ec anh, HLV Ernesto Valverde bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sang c\u00f2n 2 v\u1edbi Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Luis Suarez song h\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-atletico-madrid-180-182614.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/22/barca-muon-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-atletico-madrid.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-atletico-madrid-180-182614.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid</span><br>\r\n<span>Barca mua Griezmann, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 Ousmane Dembele theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Don Balon \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3><strong>3 CLB mua Ousmane Dembele trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi</strong></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Barca v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-atletico-madrid-180-182614.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Dembele</strong></span>, \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n h\u1ecd l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1ea1o &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; v\u1edbi Antoine Griezmann. Theo nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Blaugrana \u0111ang x\u00fac ti\u1ebfn chi 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu, theo th\u00f4ng tin Bongda24h.vn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n 3 CLB Ousmane Dembele c\u1ee7a Barca. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Atletico Madrid. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n can thi\u1ec7p v\u00e0o th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Barca ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Griezmann nh\u01b0ng hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c &ldquo;ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p&rdquo; \u0111\u1ec3 Dembele di chuy\u1ec3n theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dembele vs Malaga\" title=\"Dembele vs Malaga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/bom-tan-dembele-muon-roi-barca-o-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>3 CLB mua Dembele c\u1ee7a Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ebf \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Atletico chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t sao s\u00e1ng, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay v\u1edbi Alexis Sanchez v\u00e0 Philippe Coutinho trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng &ldquo;\u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1eddi&rdquo; trong m\u00f9a t\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm Dembele c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1ea1i Barca. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/xuat-hien-rao-can-cho-chuyen-nhuong-barca-mua-griezmann-180-182919.html\">Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n cho Barca trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mua Griezmann</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/barca-danh-bat-chelsea-de-chieu-mo-luke-shaw-184-182902.html\">Barca \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1eadt Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Luke Shaw</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/messi-muon-barca-mua-sao-liverpool-thay-vi-griezmann-180-182889.html\">Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua sao Liverpool thay v\u00ec Griezmann</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tu-choi-cam-ket-voi-barca-umtiti-se-sang-man-united-172-182867.html\">T\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i cam k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Barca, Umtiti s\u1ebd sang Man United?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-nham-sao-barca-thay-emre-can-172-182804.html\">Liverpool nh\u1eafm sao Barca thay Emre Can</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"536","checkdouble":"182979"},{"date":"11:00 28/03","title":"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n, Isco l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/28/toa-sang-o-doi-tuyen-isco-len-tieng-chi-trich-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;