\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eden Hazard s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Conte th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Da trai so truong, Eden Hazard phat bieu ve Antonio Conte hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e1 tr\u00e1i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Eden Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/5/Da-trai-so-truong,-Eden-Hazard-phat-bieu-ve-Antonio-Conte-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 trung phong \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 trung phong \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 anh ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. D\u00f9 Hazard th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 9, nh\u01b0ng HLV Conte v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu thay \u0111\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/eden-hazard-muon-lap-tuc-thoat-khoi-dia-nguc-chelsea-172-181459.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Hazard c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac</strong></span>, anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ch\u1ec9 khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Giroud v\u00e0 Morata \u0111\u00e1 trung phong c\u00f2n Hazard tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Eden Hazard s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/eden-hazard-44350.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Eden Hazard</strong></span> ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Conte, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 HLV y\u00eau c\u1ea7u: \u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng, nh\u01b0ng khi HLV mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 9, s\u1ed1 10 mi\u1ec5n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hazard va Conte\" title=\"Hazard v\u00e0 Conte\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/5/hazard-noi-gi-khi-khong-duoc-da-dung-so-truong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Eden Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Conte</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201c\u1ede \u0110T B\u1ec9, t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, HLV Roberto Martinez n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 t\u00f4i ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng. \u1ede Chelsea \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m, nh\u01b0ng khi Conte mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng\u201d, Eden Hazard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antonio Conte.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: \u201cT\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. L\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/chelsea-6.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Chelsea</strong></span> v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup v\u00e0 v\u00e0o Top 4 Premier League, sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf VCK World Cup 2018. T\u00f4i c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Eden Hazard \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/27583-40942/033100\" target=\"_blank