da gi\u1ebft sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Man City.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 gi\u1eefa Man City v\u1edbi Crystal Palace h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 12 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/sterling-muon-duoc-yeu-thuong-o-dt-anh-421-182925.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Raheem Sterling</strong></span> \u0111\u00e3 su\u00fdt b\u1ecb HLV Pep Guardiola gi\u1ebft ch\u1ebft. Ch\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e2m s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Sterling c\u0169ng nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh r\u1eb1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Man City c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n nh\u1edb trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2017, Man City \u0111\u00e3 \u201ch\u00fat ch\u1ebft\u201d tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Selhurst Park c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace. H\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 may m\u1eafn l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ederson \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Raheem Sterling bi Guardiola doa giet vi phong do kem hinh anh\" title=\"Raheem Sterling b\u1ecb Guardiola d\u1ecda gi\u1ebft v\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 k\u00e9m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/sterling-bi-guardiola-doa-giet-sau-tran-vs-crystal-palace.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sterling b\u1ecb Guardiola d\u1ecda gi\u1ebft sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Palace</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-bi-chui-la-do-cho-172-182811.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Guardiola</strong></span> kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Man City n\u00f3i chung v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Sterling n\u00f3i ri\u00eang. Ch\u00ednh m\u0169i c\u00f4ng 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. \u201cGuardiola cho b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft khi n\u00e0o \u00f4ng \u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i nh\u1edb trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Crystal Palace, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng 3 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i cho Man City th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa sau khi b\u1ecb \u00f4ng \u1ea5y gi\u1ebft trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. M\u1ed9t HLV nh\u01b0 v\u1eady mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho b\u1ea1n. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 ra nh\u1eefng khuy\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sterling-muon-duoc-yeu-thuong-o-dt-anh-421-182925.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/sterling-muon-duoc-yeu-thuong-o-dt-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sterling-muon-duoc-yeu-thuong-o-dt-anh-421-182925.html\">Sterling mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf \u0110T Anh</span><br>\r\n<span>V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu gi\u1eefa Anh vs Italia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 Wembley, v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Raheem Sterling mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed5 v\u0169 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n Sterling b\u1ecb Guardiola d\u1ecda gi\u1ebft, s\u1ed1 7 c\u1ee7a Man City c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Bernardo Silva \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u00edch cho m\u00ecnh. S\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi m\u00f9a 2017/18 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Liverpool c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 m\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ghi 15 b\u00e0n, 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 26 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y l\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh, t\u00f4i c\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c\u201d, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/real-chu-y-man-city-chua-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-raheem-sterling-172-180688.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Raheem Sterling</strong></span> n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Bernardo Silva gia nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n suy ngh\u0129 khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. Ch\u00ednh ch\u00fang \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea v\u1ec1 Raheem Sterling \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/138534-40942/033100\">Raheem Sterling</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man City tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/choang-vang-voi-so-tien-man-city-dung-de-mua-isco-180-182894.html\">Cho\u00e1ng v\u00e1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Man City d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua Isco</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/liverpool-co-the-cham-dut-su-thong-tri-cua-man-city-184-182879.html\">\u201cLiverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Man City\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/john-stones-thua-nhan-dang-gap-kho-khan-o-man-city-172-182830.html\">John Stones th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-thoi-diem-aguero-roi-man-city-172-182829.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Aguero r\u1eddi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/man-city-chang-co-gi-dang-so-voi-liverpool-184-182816.html\">Man City ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 v\u1edbi Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-bi-chui-la-do-cho-172-182811.html\">Pep Guardiola b\u1ecb ch\u1eedi nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t con ch\u00f3!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"533","checkdouble":"182939"},{"date":"18:38 27/03","title":"Lazio ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n \"Pogba Serbia\" cho M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/lazio-chot-gia-ban-pogba-serbia-cho-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;