i-corner-tr{border-top-right-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-left,.ui-corner-bl{border-bottom-left-radius:4px}.ui-corner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, Lazio \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 150 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t Serie A \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia \u0111ang l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Lazio, anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng khi v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kha nang MU mua Milinkovic-Savic dang rat kho khan hinh anh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU mua Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/27/lazio-chot-gia-ban-pogba-serbia-cho-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mua Milinkovic-Savic n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nT\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 26 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. MU mua Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMichael Carrick \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Fellaini v\u00e0 Pogba \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i, Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ef1c cao, \u00f4ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chi \u0111\u1eadm cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lazio quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 MU</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mua Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00ean 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Real v\u00e0 Barca c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic cua Lazio\" title=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic cua Lazio\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/25/Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic-cua-Lazio.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lazio h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 150 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Sergej Milinkovic-Savic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u00e3 chi \u0111\u1eadm cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Theo Corriere dello Sport, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/lazio-48.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Lazio</strong></span>, \u00f4ng Lotito bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLazio \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 150 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi M.U b\u1edfi con s\u1ed1 m\u00e0 Lazio \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/sergej-milinkovic-savic-53216.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Milinkovic-Savic </strong></span>v\u1edbi Lazio c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Serie A c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp. N\u1ebfu Lazio kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/manchester-united-1.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>M.U</strong></span> s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Marco Verratti c\u1ee7a PSG ho\u1eb7c Arturo Vidal c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"532","checkdouble":"182950"}]}